    Return a fully-structured empty canonical package.
    Matches contract-package.schema.json structure.
    Used as the base dict that merge_engine populates.
    """
    return {
        "parties": {
            "client": {"name": "", "signatories": []},
            "vendor": {"name": "", "signatories": []},
        },
